Sophisticated citrus essences and bold wood notes combine to create a refreshing composition that simultaneously endows the characteristic men's fragrance with greater lightness and strength.

Inspired by the legacy of HUGO Man– an iconic fragrance for a generation of trailblazers who aspire to live their dreams – HUGO introduces HUGO ICED: a powerful new fragrance set to encourage millennials to embrace the fresh potential of every day.

 A unique blend of invigorating icy ingredients, HUGO ICED comprises the ultimate fusion to empower the wearer to take on the adventures of a daring and expanding world. It creates unlimited opportunities for inspiring and life-changing experiences, whilst evoking the uniquely bold and irreverent nature of HUGO.

This sporty cologne is bursting with citrus, spicy and woody accords that give the scent a powerfully refreshing tone perfect for any ambitious and confident man of today. Top notes of bergamot, orange, violet leaf and green basil present an energizing, botanical aroma that’s appealing to anyone in the room. Meanwhile, heart notes of spicy cardamom, pink pepper, cinnamon and nutmeg enhance the blend with an exotic, Oriental touch that’s enigmatic and robust. Finally, base notes of sandalwood, white musk, vetiver and various woody accents dry down the other ingredients for a wholesome, masculine fragrance that’s an essential accessory for any working man’s fast-paced lifestyle.
HUGO Just Different is for the man who takes inspiration from everything around him.
HUGO Man fragrance is for men who want to live their life on their own terms.
BOSS Orange Man the new fragrance for free-spirit men who live life with optimism and passion
Top notes are metallic notes, grapefruit, pink pepper and galbanum; middle notes are rhubarb, cedar, pineapple and metallic notes; base notes are tonka bean and amber.

A refreshing blend of citruses, spices and woods, the Boss Selection Eau de Toilette Spray is for the true fragrance connoisseur. This 2006 launch perfume for men opens with citrusy notes of Mandarin Orange, Grapefruit and Bergamot, with Pink Pepper adding a rosy nuance at the top. The heart is stunning and aromatic with rich and zesty scents of Star Anise, Cedar, and Geranium for a deep and scintillating feeling. The Hugo Boss perfume dries down to notes of Vetiver, Musk, and Patchouli for a masculine aroma that lingers on.

Ooze confidence and feel like a true boss every day with Boss the Scent by Hugo Boss. Spicy and fruity notes combine to create this bold men’s fragrance, first introduced in 2015. Top notes of ginger blend perfectly with soothing lavender and crisp manika fruit at the heart, with leather base notes contributing to a rich, aromatic finish. Wear this masculine scent to make a statement wherever you go, as its rugged, earthy composition is sure to turn a few heads.

Command the attention of any room with Hugo XY, a bold eau de toilette for men. This ultra-masculine scent, which was launched by Hugo Boss in 2007, exudes the thrill and excitement of a new challenge. Cedar and bergamot top notes set an authoritative tone from the beginning, and middle notes of basil and mint bring in a cool sophistication. The fragrance dries down to patchouli notes, which bring in a touch of sensuality and a distinct complexity.

A fresh fragrance composed with delicate, light flowers combined with rose and lotus.
When Flower meets Water. A FRESH floral aquatic with a woody trail.

When the drop blossoms into a delicate petal.
A luminous Eau de toilette, created from a mandarin illuminating a radiant petal heart with a musky trail.
The morning dewdrop reveals a heart of neroli, rose and lily of the valley petals
Musky notes are spread by ambergris.

A fresh, vibrant and elegant Eau de Toilette.
A timeless fragrance with a very masculine signature.
When the vibrating freshness of Yuzu meets Sandalwood.
A new fragrance taking its inspiration from water, as a masculine symbol of strength and movement. Water, in a major key. The evocation of a salty wood. Designed by water.

Bring the clarity and warmth of Jaguar Classic Amber to your daily fragrance rotation. Released in 2011, this men’s eau de toilette features top notes of ripe petit grain and spicy pink pepper, instantly awakening the senses and bringing atypical aspects to the typical men’s fragrance. Ripe Granny Smith apple lies in the heart, adding tartness and sweetness. Finally, gourmand vanilla plays with rugged leather for playful contrast, making Jaguar Classic Amber an unexpected classic that has a place in every modern man’s scent collection.

Scandal is a new kind of fragrance for women: the elegant aura that it leaves in her wake is sullied by the Pigalle spirit beloved by Jean Paul Gaultier. Even Madam Minister is tempted by this scent of Scandal. It's more than a breath of fresh air – it’s a breath of freedom.

The rich fragrance of Jean Paul Gaultier Le Male Eau De Toilette reflects man’s complex nature. A unique blend of contrasting scents, this fragrance for men launched in 1995 from the house of Jean Paul Gaultier. Presented as a spray, the fragrance composition starts with bold fresh mint and sweet lavender and then shifts to a heart of spicy cinnamon sweetened with orange blossom. The complex base notes include smooth vanilla. Men who are not afraid to show their strength and vulnerability wear this scent with confidence to any event during any season.

Joop! Homme is a go-to signature fragrance for the confident man, bold enough to jazz up your social life during a night on the town, and low-key enough to be your daily scent. The opening notes are crisp and delicious, including juicy mandarin, sparkling lemon and tart lime. Nutty cardamom makes an appearance in the heart, while warm patchouli adds cohesion to the base. Developed in 1989 by Joop!, this men’s eau de toilette spray is the perfect blend of fresh and exotic.

Kenzo World Intense by Kenzo is a Floral Fruity Gourmand fragrance for women. This is a new fragrance. Kenzo World Intense was launched in 2017. Kenzo World Intense was created by Francis Kurkdjian and Maïa Lernout. Top note is plum
column8: middle notes are peony and jasmine

column7: Summer is all about being casual yet upbeat, and your fragrance should reflect that attitude. Wear this fragrance from Lacoste on a trip to the farmer’s market or for a picnic by the beach. Lacoste Eau De Lacoste L.12.12 Pour Elle, introduced in 2018, opens bright and happy with notes of grapefruit, mandarin orange, and pink pepper.
This original female fragrance is naturally elegant and sporty much like the Lacoste brand. It symbolizes spontaneous beauty, easiness, and freedom of the scent and the woman

Lacoste Pour Femme, the sporty-elegant female fragrance from 2003, is getting its warmer Eau de Parfum Intense interpretation in 2018, after the Eau de Parfum Légère version from 2017. The new composition is floral, velvety and woody. It is inspired by the attitude of a strong personality without arrogance, a combination of softness and strength, self-confidence and elegance. Top notes include the subtle aroma of caramel, representing the tan colour of the packaging. The floral heart preserves floral notes of Bulgarian rose from the original, as well as the signature notes of Himalayan cedar and sandalwood at the base.

Lacoste introduces Touch of Pink, a fragrance for ”vitality filled, dynamic women”. For the women with a real zest for life, who are genuine and spontaneous. An intriguing fresh, fruity floral fragrance.
Lacoste Essential is about freedom to play&enjoy life

Men who want to display the ultimate in timeless sophistication wear the fragrance of Lacoste Eau De Lacoste L.12.12 Blanc. This pure eau de toilette scent launched in 2011 from the enduring French fashion house of Rene Lacoste. Blanc, which is French for white, describes the clean, simple crispness of this fragrance. Opening notes featuring fresh grapefruit yield to a heart of creamy tuberose and sweet ylang-ylang. Aromas of Virginia cedar and smooth leather provide an elegant finish. Wear this masculine scent to keep your cool on hot summer days.

The Lacoste Eau de Lacoste L.12.12 Bleu Powerful Eau de Toilette Spray for men invigorates the senses and boosts feelings of freshness and vigor. Introduced in 2011, this masculine fragrance features a cooling and aromatic blend of Mint and Grapefruit at the top. The heart is ruled by striking and intense whiffs of African Orange Flower and Sage that induce raw sensuality. Earthy and woody notes of Patchouli, Fern, and Virginia Cedar entwine at the base and lend a lasting trail to this Lacoste perfume.

Cooling and refreshing, the Lacoste Eau de Lacoste L.12.12 Noir Intense Eau de Toilette Spray for men is an ideal fragrance to wear through the spring and summer evenings. Launched in the year 2013, this Lacoste perfume opens with fresh and aqueous notes of Watermelon at the top. Lively and peppery Basil blends with citrusy Verbena and aromatic Lavender at the heart and lends an invigorating feeling. Dark Chocolate, Cashmeran, Coumarin, and Patchouli merge at the base of the perfume for a bitter-sweet masculine fragrance.

A woody spicy scent, L’HOMME LACOSTE captures the inimitable heritage of René Lacoste, elegantly ignoring the rules to being free from convention. The fragrance’s structure reveals the sides of the modern LACOSTE man.

The Lacoste Live Eau de Toilette reinvents the traditional codes of Lacoste, mixing sporty heritage and French elegance with a fresh, colourful edge. Inspired by the innovative spirit of Rene Lacoste, Lacoste Live bursts with energy and momentum. It’s a distinctive,creative fragrance, perfectly suited to creative, irreverent men with a fresh perception on the world. An Ideal Summer Fragrance !!!

A distinctly fresh and masculine scent with a sophisticated edge, Lacoste Pour Homme's plum and apple top notes give a fresh and sensual hook to the fragrance, while spicy elements infuse energy and masculinity, and musk and Jamaican rum make the fragrance warm, sexy, and long lasting.

Jasmins Marzipane by Lancome is a Woody Floral Musk fragrance for women and men. This is a new fragrance. Jasmins Marzipane was launched in 2016. The nose behind this fragrance is Dominique Ropion. The fragrance features jasmine sambac, jasmine, almond wood, bourbon vanilla, sandalwood, musk and cashmere wood.

La vie est belle is a French expression meaning "life is beautiful". Incarnated by Julia Roberts, La vie est belle is a universal declaration to the beauty of life. A unique olfactory signature with the noblest ingredients of Concrete of Iris Pallida, Jasmine Sambac, Orange Blossom and Patchouli Essence.

column3: La Vie Est Belle "Bouquet De Printemps"
column7: A floral fragrance for woman. Features bergamot, jasmine sambac and orange blossom.

It took them two years to create a new Eau de Parfum, La vie est belle L’Éclat, that expresses how happiness is magnified the more widely it is shared. The fragrance unveils crisp head notes on a soft and generous base, bathed in the radiant freshness of orange blossom. This flower is at the heart of this particular story, both reminiscent of La vie est belle, and yet totally new.
Miracle eau de parfum women’s fragrance from designer Lancome. Miracle is classified as a modern, warm, light, sophisticated fragrance. Fragrance Notes: amber, freesia, ginger, magnolia, Pepper.

column3: Tresor La Nuit Tresor a la Folie
column7: This rich and exquisite women’s perfume was crafted by two master perfumers who combined their craftsmanship to create La Nuit Trésor Eau de Parfum. Beginning with a burst of delicious raspberry, the notes of a Damascena rose have then been enhanced to give the fragrance a deep and mysterious scent. Vanilla, grown on the petals of an orchid in Tahiti, gives the fragrance a solar and radiant note.

From the design house of Marc Jacobs, Daisy was introduced in 2007, an ultra-feminine fragrance for women that delights the senses and serves as the ideal everyday scent. From the first whiff, Daisy intoxicates as fresh violet leaf, uplifting blood grapefruit and sweet strawberry notes float around you. Floral notes, including captivating gardenia, make up the romantic heart of the fragrance. An earthy base provides an air of intrigue, swirling with enchanting and mysterious musk notes.

Light and airy, daisy dream is both floral and fruity. The top has a juicy fruitiness that is playful and fun. he heart imparts a rich, feminine jasmine, notes of lychee and blue wisteria. A dreamy drydown of white woods, musks and coconut water.
A bouquet of lush jasmine with accents of creamy woods. Overtly feminine and head-turning.
A spotlight on warm amber wrapped in sandalwood, layered with white flowers. Sumptious and deeply seductive.

For a bright floral experience, spray on the fragrance of Very Hollywood by Michael Kors. New York designer Michael Kors partnered with Estee Lauder to launch this sophisticated eau de parfum for women in 2009. Embodying strength and elegance, this feminine scent starts with notes of sweet mandarin orange and zesty frozen bergamot. A heart featuring moist jasmine and exotic ylang-ylang gains support from base notes including creamy amber, creating a smooth scent in the dry down. Wear this very special fragrance as the perfect complement to your spring and summer wardrobe.

EMBLEM is a rock, a landmark, an identity. From the World renowned luxury brand comes a fragrance for the man who is refined but powerful, with strong presence and attraction. A fresh, woody aromatic, EMBLEM bursts open with bitter grapefruit, icy cardamom and clary sage leaf, warmed by black peppercorns.

Crisp frosted violet leaves wrapped in cinnamon leaves form the heart, while intense precious woods and Tonka beans unveil a unique dry down. The craftsmanship of Montblanc pens is echoed in every aspect in EMBLEM from the masculine fragrance to the modern packaging, deep black with intense shine

Turn heads wherever you go when you make Mont Blanc Legend men’s eau de toilette spray your go-to scent. Created in 2011, this fragrance features top notes of bergamot and pineapple that give it a sweet essence. Notes of lavender and geranium lend a fresh, floral scent to this fragrance, helping to invigorate your senses and providing an energetic start to your day. A sandalwood base note give this scent a woody finish that lingers behind as you pass by and stays with you well into the evening.

Montblanc Legend Night is a magnetic woody fragrance, a warm masculine scent that will reveal the inner charisma of the man who wears it. Mysterious and reassuring. The Eau de Parfum brings out the elegance and aura of the Legend Night man.

Feel a surge in energy levels with the masculine fragrance of Mont Blanc Legend Spirit Eau De Toilette. If you have a zest for life, the effervescent composition of Grapefruit, Pink Pepper, and Bergamot at the top will blow your mind. The heart is infused with the intense scents of Lavender and Cardamom for day long freshness. Wear it for a few hours and a woody aroma will fill your heart with base notes of Cashmere Woods, Sandalwood, Oakmoss, and White Musk for a hint of sensuality and unmistakable elegance.

The Alien bottle holding this elixir is reminiscent of a sacred stone. Jewel-like, its facets express the radiance of the mysterious.
Bold scents full of character and original combinations. It's instantly recognizable and always unforgettable.

Launched in January 2018, Alien Flora Futura is an optimistic and light Eau de Toilette for women . The fragrance opens with woody notes of Buddha accord with citron. The unique floral scent of Queen of the Night blossoms in the heart carrying into the base. Notes of sandalwood and white amber ground the scent for an overall woody and floral fragrance. The pink bottle captures the unique essence contained within with the artistic detail, gold accents and interesting shape.

Half-god, half-man, experience an
extraordinary adventure where serenity meets power.
An assertive and irresistible fragrance, leather and cashmeran wood transform you into a MUGLER man, while a hint of Osmanthus ties it in with its alter ego, Alien. An exquisite bottle with a masculine design in synergy with Alien.

The for her signature heart of musc is surrounded by roses, spices, and amber wood, to create a sparkling fragrance.
A vibrant and assertive pink bottle and box.

Black XS for Her Eau de Parfum is announced as an oriental-woody composition with fruity and floral accords, which does not deviate much from the original pyramid. It starts with a combination of cranberries and the flower of the exotic tropical tree Tamarind. The heart combines the floral notes of black violet and Hellebore rose, after which the base brings notes of massoia wood and black vanilla.

The popular black wave also splashed the famous Paco Rabanne Black XS collection, but not in totality, because the female bottles were not presented so darkly until now. In July 2013,Paco Rabanne is launching the new limited duo named Black XS L’Aphrodisiaque, designed in black matte bottles and touched with modern rock details in gold. The popular shapes of the bottles are emboldened with golden skulls and trendy studs.
An oriental floral fragrance for woman. Top notes are neroli and black pepper; middle notes are jasmin, rose and night blooming cereus; base notes are vanille and cahmere wood.

Paco Rabanne launches two new editions of its edgy fragrant collection Black XS. After the original Black XS fragrances from 2005 and 2007, Black XS L’Exces from 2012 and Black XS L’Aphrodisiaque from 2013, new duo called Black XS Potion appears in February 2014. These new fragrances, conceived as true love elixirs, are developed by perfumers Olivier Cresp and Emilie Coppermann. Black XS Potion for Her opens with zesty accords of grapefruit, which leads to the heart of red Baccara roses and pink hellebore. The base features warm extract of black sandalwood and amber.
Lady MILLION. Diamond-bright because decadence is thrilling. A trail of white flowers awakens the skin with fresh notes and exudes an intimate woody warmth.

Hack the life of your dreams. Life is a game!
Seek out sensations. No limits.
Create your own luck as you go. Don’t wait.

Lady MILLION LUCKY.
A euphoric flower in every way: sparkling, vibrant, addictive.
With a dash of insolence and sandalwood.
An audacious rose

A modern day goddess. Heaven-scent. Iconic, chic. Unique. Half-myth, half-muse. Smiling on victory as her natural reward. Ready to seduce Zeus. Trouble in paradise... A sensuel salty-vanilla, earthly, irrresistible.
Olympéa reaches her peak. Newly victorious and glorious. A sensual salty-vanilla newly fused with deep amber. Carnal and irresistible. Touching hitherto unreached dizzy heights.

Pure XS for her. Excess in its purest state. A floral with a wild orgasmic bite. Ylang-ylang unleashes its raw erotica into the heat of hot vanilla. Audaciously devastating, viciously liber-ating, popcorn that packs a punch. 24/7 addiction. Popped puffed corn, musk, and milkwood notes ignite the skin. Desire-on-fire.

1 MILLION. The scent of success. Going for gold because decadence is thrilling. Not-so-gentle man. An intoxicating, powerful blend that starts out fresh and moves onto a spicy leather accord. An arresting alchemy of full-on seduction.
The party's private and the game is on. Roll the dice. Too late for nice. Break the bank. Escape to the other side. Illicitly addictive. Delectable.
Charming, uncompromising, just radiating the vibe of his sex-appeal. Hitting a fresh note that takes in the rough with the smooth, before living it all - raw and free.

For the summer season of July 2013, the house of Paco Rabanne has released a new limited edition pair branded by the name Black XS L’Aphrodisiaque, housed in black matte perfume containers accented with contemporary rock aspects colored in metallic gold. The fashionable bottles designs are highlighted with golden skulls and funky fashionable spikes.

Make a lasting impression on those around you with the inimitable, intoxicating fragrance of the Black XS L?Exces Eau de Toilette Intense Spray from Paco Rabanne. Created in the year 2012, this perfume for men captivates the senses with strong, alluring scents of Lavender and Amalfi Lemon at the top. Woody-earthy whiff of Cypriol Oil combines with cooling sea notes in the middle for a fresh and vibrant feeling. Patchouli and Amber add warmth to the base of this masculine fragrance and ensure a unique olfactory journey.

Dedicated to the city of LA, one of the nation’s biggest music hubs, and used musky, fruity and warm ingredients to convey the dynamic industry that is rock. Top notes include sunny oranges, clary sage and tart lemon; middle notes of cinnamon, apple, lily-of-the-valley and pineapple soften the stronger ingredients; and base notes of coumarin, oak moss andvanilla bring a much-needed balance to the mixture.

Charm everyone with confidence when you wear the Invictus Aqua Eau De Toilette. Designed by Paco Rabane for a man who is always calm and collected, the 2016 fragrance reveals freshness at the top with Grapefruit, Yuzu and Pink Pepper. Creating a lasting impression, the fragrance is resplendent in the middle with notes from Sea Water and Violet Leaf. The scent dries down to a crisp, woody and elegant base of Guaiac Wood, Amberwood and Ambergris for a fragrance that will not be easily forgotten.
INVICTUS. Stronger than before. Vibrant, vital, vigorous. Galvanised for battle. Tempting…Fate and more.

Invictus, the scent of victory the essence of heroes. Ecstatically addictive, a powerful adrenalin shot for serial winners. Power, courage, victory distilled into a daring smash-up of freshness and heat. When you’re in it to win.
First "aromatic fougère" and future icon. The smell of freshly shaved skin, on a honeyed tobacco background. The insane charm of a classic. Manly, subtle.

To have it all. In excess.Devastatingly fascinating. Intensely nonchalant. Girls fall under his spell. Now’s the time to lighten up, play with fire. Lose control. An untamed Oriental, hot and fresh. Excess in its purest state.
Experience the chic and sexy fragrance by Paris Hilton for women. This sheer floral fragrance is feminine and sexy to be worn day or night.
The composition includes an elegant mix of musk in the top, a sensual balsamic vanillic accord of benzoin in the heart and sweet modern caramel in the base of the fragrance.

The design house of Ralph Lauren expands its Romance fragrance line with Midnight Romance for women, an alluring scent that is suitable for any season. Spray it on your skin, and let your senses be swept away by notes of raspberry and vanilla that are expertly mixed with freesia, bergamot and exotic litchi for a fragrance that is fruity and sweet with a hint of woodsy musk. Spray it on in the morning, and let the scent lift your spirits throughout the day.”

Is an Aromatic Fougere fragrance for men. Polo Blue was launched in 2003. Polo Blue was created by Carlos Benaim and Christophe Laudamiel. Top notes are melon, mandarin orange and cucumber; middle notes are basil, sage and geranium; base notes are musk, woodsy notes and suede.
Polo Red is a fiery blend of spicy red saffron, fresh red grapefruit and deep redwood that ignites the thrill seeker in every man.

Polo Red White & Blue is a men’s aromatic fragrance that was presented in 2009 . It has aromatic, ozonic, aquatic, fruity, fresh spicy, and sweet main accords. Ideal for spring and summer day wear, the fragrance has moderate longevity and sillage. Head notes of cucumber and red apple begin the symphony, moving to heart notes of lavender and sage. Base notes of musk and woodsy notes end the performance.
A fragrance for the man & woman who never goes unnoticed

Graceful sensuality and sassy femininity is what characterizes the Signorina Eau De Parfum Spray. Elegant and charming, the perfume was introduced in the year 2011 by the design house Salvatore Ferragamo. Timeless modernity and Italian charm oozes out from the top notes that are a medley of Red Currant and Pink Pepper. The middle notes arrives with the seductive and harmonious blend of Rose, Jasmine and Peony. The end notes of Patchouli, Musk and Panacotta elegantly close this unique fragrance.

Alien Eau de Parfum: The original and unique Alien fragrance.
A floral, woody, amber creation originating from the bold excessiveness of two powerful notes (cashmeran and amber) brightened by a sun flower (sambac jasmine). The olfactory expression of radiation and splendour. The fragrance bottle is like a gem, concealing the secret of Alien

The uniqueness of Angel, reinterpreted. Like the original fragrance, this unique oriental-gourmand comes to life with an addictive scent. It features the same Carl sensuality, yet it's more subtly provocative, rounded, and finely nuanced

Angel Pure Wood Cologne by Thierry Mugler, Evoking the aroma of wood slivers and earthy spices with a tinge of coffee, Angel Pure Wood by Thierry Mugler emits the scent of traditional masculinity. Launched in 2014, the men’s fragrance was a limited edition offering based off of the incredibly popular Angel fragrance, which was originally released in 1996. Crafted for connoisseurs of the wild, the scent harnesses the untamed energy of nature and pairs it with the refinement of the classic cologne. The scent finds the perfect balance with a simple, yet intriguing, blend of fragrance notes that include the dry scent of the mighty oak, intense and dark coffee, comforting and familiar vanilla, dark and exotic patchouli and fresh cypress.

Allow your adventurous side to surface with A*Men, an eau de toilette that was released by Thierry Mugler in 1996. With its enticing blend of woody and fresh notes, this vibrant men’s scent awakens your inner intensity. A*Men bursts into being with top notes of bergamot and mint, enhancing your vitality and energy for life. At the heart of the fragrance, patchouli heart notes bring an earthy exhilaration that lasts as the scent dries down to memorable notes of musk and tonka bean.

Its black, opaque bottle is characteristic for is narrow relief creases, created to follow the style of numerous Tom Ford collection editions, but it brings us a completely new shape. The golden color stopper follows its dimensions and form, and is also of characteristic design.

Let your mind and body flourish under the sweet, blooming decadence of Tom Ford Orchid Soleil . This intoxicating perfume blends citrus, green and aromatic accords for a chic and satisfying aroma that will leave you feeling beautiful and refreshed for hours after application. Top notes of bitter orange, spicy pink pepper and crisp cypress introduce the scent with a burst of energy and intensity unlike anything you’ve ever experienced. Heart notes of breezy tuberose and breezy red spider lily incorporate a rejuvenating, floral bouquet that’s pleasantly feminine and sophisticated.

Introducing Velvet Orchid Lumière, a bright, shimmering shade of the ultra-feminine signature scent.

Spellbinding and fresh, the new interpretation of the Velvet Orchid Eau de Parfum immerses you in its gourmand-touched sensuality.

Violet Blonde, glamorous and sophisticated, opens with violet leaf, Italian mandarin and pink pepper. The center piece of the composition consists of Tuscan iris absolute, Tuscan orris butter, Sambac jasmine and sampaquita. The base is home to elegant and sophisticated tones of musk, suede, cedar, vetiver and benzoin.

Tom Ford Extreme is a fragrance that was released in 2007 . The scent opens with top notes of basil, chamomile, cardamom, coriander, cinnamon, citrus, and lemon. The heart of the fragrance contains fig , plum, saffron, sandalwood, thyme, violet, and cedar wood. It closes with a base of balsam fir, caramel, leather, patchouli, rum, truffle, vanilla, vetiver, and frankincense.

Indulge in the richness of opulence with the Tom Ford Eau De Toilette Spray for men. Launched in the year 2013 by the design house Tom Ford, the fragrance is bold and alluring. Lavish in the top notes are Citruses, Italian Lemon and Mint. The center comes to life with Oriental Notes, Spices and Herbal Notes. This sensual combination alight the Woody Notes at the base creating an empowering scent along with Musk.

Command the attention you desire with Noir, the bold eau de parfum launched by the Tom Ford design house in 2012. Designed for the confident man, Noir opens on invigorating notes of juicy bergamot and lemony verbena, quickly heating up at the heart, where spicy black pepper is calmed by the sweet nuances of nutmeg. Settling into a comfortable warmth, this sophisticated men’s scent features soothing amber notes on the dry down that are familiar and long-lasting.

POLISHED. DARK. REFLECTIVE.

Tom Ford Noir Anthracite reflects the light in the dark, the brilliance of bergamot and spice against rich black woods. The duality of the Noir man mirrors the dynamic tension between contrasts, where the high-shine glare against grey metal and the black veins of macassar pour into primal night.

Stand out from the crowd with the enigmatic and sensational Tom Ford Noir Extreme, a daring men’s cologne . This strong and inviting fragrance blends spicy, citrus, floral and gourmand accords for a delectable and charming aroma that’s sure to get you noticed anywhere from the office to the sports bar. Top notes of citrus mandarin orange oil, fresh green neroli, warm nutmeg, spicy saffron essence and cardamom opens the scent with a grand, Oriental atmosphere that’s zesty and energetic. Middle notes of light orange blossom, night-blooming jasmine, elegant rose absolute and a mastic composition combine with the sweet Indian kulfi dessert for a delicious and tantalizing elixir. Completing the fragrance are base notes of Indian sandalwood, warm amber liquid, creamy vanilla and various woody notes for a smooth, comforting balance that winds down the intensity and illuminates every ingredient flawlessly.

Vast. Untethered. Driven.

Freedom comes from within, the desert heart of the west wrapped in leather. It moves forward, untethered, through the still air of wide-open space. Dust on wind, skin on skin, ombré leather reveals itself like a landscape in layers, where stretches of rock transform into sunrise blonde low on the horizon

Luxurious and extravagant, Black Orchid eau de parfum spray is the ideal choice for women who appreciate the finer things in life. Launched in 2015 by the Tom Ford fragrance design house, this fragrance opens on top notes of citrusy bergamot and sweet ylang-ylang, so you feel fresh from the first spritz. At the heart, the fragrance’s namesake, black orchid, offers a soft, floral quality, while a base of patchouli and vetiver provides a more natural finish.

Make no mistake ? the name Oud Wood Tom Ford tells you what you need to know about this eau de parfum for men and women. Multifaceted clothing and accessories designer, filmmaker and fragrance developer Tom Ford launched this unisex scent in 2007 as part of his Private Blend collection. Ford created this unique, long-lasting fragrance spray to wear alone or to layer with other scents in the 12-fragrance collection. Oud Wood blends smoky, rich oud (agarwood) with robust notes including Brazilian rosewood, creamy sandalwood, slightly nutty cardamom and smooth vanilla.

Tom Ford Tobacco Oud is a women’s and men’s woody spicy fragrance with tobacco, warm spicy, whiskey, oud,and sweet main accords. Launched in 2013, this scent was created by perfumer Olivier Gillotin of Givaudan. It has a top note of whiskey, followed by middle notes of cinnamon, spicy notes, and coriander. The base notes contain tobacco, oud, sandalwood, patchouli, benzoin, incense, vanilla, and cedar. With long-lasting longevity and moderate sillage, this fragrance works best on fall and winter evenings.

Tommy Girl by Tommy Hilfiger is a floral, fruity fragrance for women. Tommy Girl portrays today's young woman: lively, independent and natural. Fresh top notes are black currant, camelia, mandarin orange and apple tree blossom; young, energizing middle notes are honeysuckle, lily, violet, mint, grapefruit, citruses and rose. The sensual base note is created with magnolia, rose, sandalwood, jasmine and cedarwood.

Bring the smooth accords of this Italian chypre botanical fragrance to your daily scent rotation with its expert composition of feminine and unisex elements. A 2015 release by Valentino, this women’s scent opens with refreshing bergamot, with ultra-feminine rose lying just underneath. Patchouli and leather offer a complex element of masculinity to this women’s fragrance, making it the go-to choice for women who love the balance inherent in androgyny. At the same time, gourmand vanilla soothes the senses and restores femininity in the final note.

Versace Bright Crystal is a precious jewel of rare beauty characterised by a fresh, vibrant, floral scent.

Versace Bright Crystal is inspired by a mixture of Donatella Versace's favourite floral fragrances. A fresh, sensual blend of refreshing chilled yuzu and pomegranate mingled with soothing blossoms of peony, magnolia, and lotus flower, warmed with notes of musk and amber.

Versace Bright Crystal is a precious jewel of rare beauty characterised by a fresh, vibrant, floral scent.

Versace Bright Crystal is inspired by a mixture of Donatella Versace's favourite floral fragrances. A fresh, sensual blend of refreshing chilled yuzu and pomegranate mingled with soothing blossoms of peony, magnolia, and lotus flower, warmed with notes of musk and amber.

Absolute sensuality. Absolute transparency. Absolute brightness. An absolute temptation. Versace introduces Bright Crystal Absolu, the intense version of one of the most beloved jewel-fragrances in the world, where the essence of Bright Crystal is enhanced to the extreme. A fragrance made even more intoxicating by its enhanced olfactory concentrations and prolonged persistence. For a woman who entrusts her femininity to the timeless seductive power of Bright Crystal, in harmony with Versace glamour.

Versace Crystal Noir is a fragrance for the true Versace woman. A magical perfume, sheer and sensual at the same time and leaves a lasting impression.

Versace Crystal Noir is a fragrance for the true Versace woman. A magical fragrance: ethereal yet carnal, precious, delicate and persistent. It has an ultra-feminine, oriental-floral scent.

Uniqueness. Strength. Sensuality and Elegance. An alchemy of alluring notes dance, seduce, and come together in an elegant embrace.

An alchemy of irresistible notes that dance, arouse, come together, and embrace, this fragrance is a refreshing blackcurrant sorbet with Granny Smith apple and a contemporary floral bouquet. Woody base notes playfully mix together to create a unique, captivating, sensuous, and vibrant movement.

Eros Pour Femme Eau de Toilette captures the primal power of a woman in a radiant, sensual essence. A fragrance of strength, individuality and seduction.

The primal power of a woman, captured in a radiant, sensual essence. A fragrance of strength, individuality and seduction. Eros pour Femme Eau de Toilette is a new sensual and addictive freshness based on the combination of notes of fine citrus fruits, heady floral petals, and sensual woods.

Making its fragrant debut in 2011, Yellow Diamond eau de toilette by Versace is a light, fresh scent for women that wears well in summer and has the discreet character of an everyday fragrance. The top notes include bright and vibrant Amalfi lemon, bergamot and neroli with a sweet touch of pear, and the scent continues on the same fruity-floral theme with African orange flower hints. Despite its invigorating quality, this scent succeeds in retaining a luxurious vibe and is fittingly encased in a spray bottle evoking the radiant colors of summer and the glamor of diamonds.

Dylan Blue is a highly distinctive fougère fragrance. The expression of a man's strength and charisma, conveying modern and sensual Mediterranean freshness.

Dylan Blue is the new fragrance that captivates the sensual scents of the Mediterranean. Woody notes of ambrox evoke tradition, while exquisite citrus notes of bergamot and grapefruit make the fragrance modern and aquatic hints add invigorating freshness. Masculine notes of black pepper, papyrus wood and incense form the fragrance's pulsating heart. The base is accentuated by a combination of seductive mineral musk, Tonka beans, and saffron- recalling a man's individuality.

The new perfume Eros is the first in the past five years to be launched and aimed at men. Donatella Versace’s desire was to fit the fragrance into the concept of the Versace brand and to depict style and significance of long-lasting design, quality and popularity. “Eros is truly the DNA of the house of Versace” – explains Donatella. “We have a Greek motive making us think about ancient Greece, antiquities and mythology, while turquoise color represents the Mediterranean. That is Versace!”

Eros interprets sublime masculinity through a luminous aura with an intense, vibrant and glowing freshness. Versace Eros is a fragrance for a strong man, passionate and master of himself.

Love, passion, beauty and desire: these are the key concepts Eros, the fragrance by Versace. The perfection of the male body is fused with the allusion to Greek mythology and classic sculpture that has characterized the Versace world since the beginning: Eros, god of love, able to make people fall in love with his bow and arrow. Versace Eros is a fragrance for a strong man, passionate and master of himself.

Versace Eros Flame the new men’s fragrance, strikes you right through the heart. Versace Eros Flame is a fragrance for a strong, passionate, self-confident man who is deeply in touch with his emotions. He simultaneously perceives present feelings and savors the eternal scent of true love. Olfactive Family: Hesperidic – Amber – Woody.

Versace Eau Fraiche is an olfactive harmony where the most classic ingredients of men’s scents are refined with unusual notes to give life to a surprisingly fresh fragrance. Smooth fruits spiced with green leaves and warm notes of musk, amber, and sycamore wood, make this a scent for today's more introspective man.

Versace Pour Homme, blends essential ingredients of Mediterranean origin to hit aromatic notes that match the man of today.

Versace Pour Homme, blends essential ingredients of Mediterranean origin to hit aromatic notes that match the man of today: knowledgeable and self-confident, he has the ability to live in harmony with the natural world. Dynamic and entrepreneurial, the Versace Pour Homme man communicates his forceful and passionate character through this decidedly masculine fragrance.

Yves Saint Laurent launches Black Opium, a rock'n'roll interpretation of the classic that should highlight the dark, mysterious side of the YSL brand.

Master perfumers Nathalie Lorson and Marie Salamagne, in collaboration with Olivier Cresp and Honorine Blanc, developed the composition. It is an aromatic fragrance with coffee, present in large quantities, dominate the scent.

Additional accords are pink pepper, orange blossom, jasmine, vanilla, patchouli and cedar.

When the electrifying energy of black coffee meets the assertive femininity of white flowers. A vibrant, sensual and addictive contrast of light and dark. Confident & bold, the Black Opium woman embodies the new Yves Saint Laurent spirit. A fragrance like a shot of adrenaline to live the illusion all night. Free and self-confident, she expresses a femininity glamourous yet impertinent. Always searching for new experiences, nothing will stop her. In this Pure Illusion edition, she is ready to live the illusion of the night. More irresistible than ever, the Black Opium Pure Ilussion bottle gets dressed for the night with a sparkling & hypnotizing series of black glitters strips in all over print.

Manifesto is a new women’s perfume from Yves Saint Laurent, coming out on the market in late August 2012. The perfume is described as spontaneous, free spirited and courageous; a scent full of passion and emotion. The composition is developed by Anne Flipo and Loc Dong. It starts off with fresh green wave, bergamot and black currant. The heart includes accords of white flowers such as Sambac jasmine and lily of the valley. The base is woody and slightly oriental and captures notes of cedar, sandalwood, vanilla and tonka bean.

Opium Eau De Toilette Spray by Yves Saint Laurent offers women a rich fragrance experience. YSL launched the original Opium in 1977, and introduced this newly packaged scent in 2009. This women’s scent features tart bergamot and honey-like mandarin orange as top notes. A heart including spicy carnation and sweet jasmine combines with a base including minty, woody patchouli to please the senses long after you spray on this fragrance. Feminine and sophisticated, this scent reveals the complexities of your personality in a special way whether you wear it day or night.

KOUROS, inspired by the gods of ancient Greece, is a fragrance of strength and triumphant masculinity. It’s a conquering spirit, the cult of the male body. The resounding note of Coriander is enhanced by the energy of Bergamot and the virile power of Artemisia.

The sensual Clove and floral notes of Jasmine then warm this complex and vibrant essence before Ambregris and Oakmoss complete the perfection of the trail.

A divine and conquering spicy chypre fragrance with a powerful and intense trail. Coriander - Clove - Oakmoss
Announces itself as citrusy – chypre – woody, made of note of bergamot, aldehydes and star anise.
Fragrance contains a mix of bergamot, pink pepper and patchouli.

Yves Saint Laurent La Nuit de l`Homme is a new masculine representative of the house of YSL and it will appear on the market in March 2009.The perfume is announced as one full of contrasts and tensions.Its flacon is dark and powerful, as if it were announcing powerful ingredients it carries in itself.
A Fresh Oriental fragrance, made of tensions and olfactory clashes, for a darkly handsome man who sweeps away everything in their path. A night full of promises...

A resounding disruption for a fragrance of excess, the first to use “oud”, the most dense and diffusive of all woods. Its essence develops a deep unambiguous presence and already contains notes of balm and amber. It merges with myrrh and cistus to create a warm, intense and fascinating trail.

Mandarin gives a top opening and delivers singular vibrancy, whereas a very potent and dense patchouli wood facet provides depth and addictive tenacity. Slightly restyled in 2010, M7 OUD ABSOLU has been enhanced with brilliant mineral freshness, revealing the full richness of expression of “oud”.

The M7 OUD ABSOLU man has raw virility and sensuality that makes him equally desirable and dangerous. NEW M7! NEW packaging, size and price.
Discover Yves Saint Laurent’s new men’s fragrance: Y, the scent of freedom. This white and dark fougere dares you to follow your passions and carve your own path. Everything starts with a why.
